title: Arbor Skateboards: Slalom Series Wheels
description:
Arbor team riders, Jimmy Riha, Aaron Bagel and Max Myers hooked up in San Diego to get in some shredding and test out Arbor's Slalom Series wheels. These rollers are smooth, the Arbor Assault skateboard is nasty and the skating is down right dirty.
Check out Arbor everywhere:
